BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Atlanta Micro Short Film Festival
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260711T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260712T000000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1707@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Film Screening
DESCRIPTION:Over 120 micro shorts in one afternoon\, each six minutes or l
 ess\, from animation to horror to documentary.\n\nA single fast-moving aft
 ernoon packed with more than 120 short films\, every one of them clocking 
 in at six minutes or under. Filmmakers from around the world contribute ac
 ross the board: animation\, horror\, documentary\, comedy\, drama\, and ex
 perimental work. Presented by 7 Stages\, in a theatre that started life as
  a movie house.
GEO:33.7639125;-84.3509364
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:7 Stages Theatre\, 1105 Euclid Ave NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://atlantafilmseries.tix.page/e/atlanta-micro-short-film-festival
END:VEVENT
