DESCRIPTION:Selina Fillinger's Broadway farce: seven women scramble to kee
 p a catastrophically inept president out of trouble.\n\nSelina Fillinger's
  2022 Broadway farce about the seven women who actually keep the White Hou
 se running. When the president's stray four-letter word snowballs from PR 
 headache into global crisis\, the beleaguered women in his orbit scramble 
 to keep him upright and the country intact. The Washington Post's critic l
 ikened it to a cross between SNL and Veep. From Live Arts Theatre\; recomm
 ended for ages 18 and up for severe language\, adult situations\, and viol
 ence.
