DESCRIPTION:Screwball comedy: a fading actress takes a TV commercial direc
 tor hostage on a snowbound Christmas Eve.\n\nIn Renée Taylor and Joseph B
 ologna's screwball comedy\, a fading actress snowed in on Christmas Eve ta
 kes a TV commercial director hostage\, angling to turn the standoff into b
 oth a romance and her big break. Taylor and Bologna\, the real-life marrie
 d team behind Lovers and Other Strangers\, originally wrote and starred in
  it themselves. Scott Ross directs for Merely Players. Runs through July 2
 6.
