SUMMARY:Grease Sing-A-Long (1978)
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260801T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260801T170000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1233@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Film Screening
DESCRIPTION:The 1978 movie musical with on-screen lyrics — sing every wo
 rd\, rated PG\, 105 minutes.\n\nThe 1978 film with John Travolta and Olivi
 a Newton-John as Danny and Sandy\, screened sing-along style with on-scree
 n lyrics for "Summer Nights\," "Greased Lightnin'\," and the rest. A summe
 r romance collides with 1950s high-school social order when the pair land 
 at the same school. Rated PG\, 1 hour 45 minutes\, and a live pre-show con
 cert on the house Mighty Allen Theatre Organ begins thirty minutes before 
 the film.
