SUMMARY:Mamma Mia! and Margaritas!
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260822T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260822T170000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1657@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Film Screening
DESCRIPTION:The 2008 ABBA movie musical on the big screen\, with a margari
 ta bar and a pre-show organ concert.\n\nThe 2008 film of the ABBA jukebox 
 musical: on a Greek island\, a bride-to-be finds three men in her mother's
  old diary who might be her father\, and quietly adds all of them to the g
 uest list — mom Donna (Meryl Streep) none the wiser. Pierce Brosnan\, Co
 lin Firth\, and Stellan Skarsgård are the candidates. The Strand Theatre 
 sells margaritas\, frozen or on the rocks\, and boas are encouraged. A liv
 e concert on the house's Mighty Allen Theatre Organ starts thirty minutes 
 before the film. 1 hour 48 minutes\, rated PG-13.
GEO:33.9536122;-84.5492054
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:The Strand Theatre\, 117 N Park Square
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://thestrand.my.salesforce-sites.com/ticket/#/instances/a0FPs0000
 075UavMAE
END:VEVENT
