UID:occ-1193@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Shakespeare's shipwreck comedy: twins separated at sea\, a wom
 an in disguise\, and a love triangle nobody can untangle.\n\nShakespeare's
  comedy of mistaken identity. Shipwrecked and separated from her twin brot
 her\, Viola disguises herself as a young man and enters Duke Orsino's serv
 ice\, only to fall for him while carrying his love letters to a countess w
 ho promptly falls for her. Meanwhile a forged letter and a pair of yellow 
 stockings send the pompous steward Malvolio into humiliating raptures. Fro
 m Pumphouse Players\, one of Georgia's oldest continuously operating commu
 nity theatre companies.
