SUMMARY:Fox Archives Day
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260823T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260823T180000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1320@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Heritage Exhibition
DESCRIPTION:The Fox opens its archives — artifacts and archival material
 s from the 1929 movie palace\, with Atlanta History Center.\n\nThe fifth a
 nnual open house of the Fox Theatre's archives\, presented with the Atlant
 a History Center. Archival materials\, artifacts\, and exhibits trace the 
 building's story\, from 1929 movie palace to the grassroots campaign that 
 saved it from demolition in the 1970s. The displays fill the Grand Salon a
 nd Egyptian Ballroom\, so browsing doubles as a look inside two of the the
 atre's ornate event spaces.
