SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Workshop or Class
DESCRIPTION:Free hands-on improv workshop from the Southside Sidekicks\, f
 irst of a Sunday series that ends in a showcase.\n\nThe Southside Sidekick
 s\, the resident improv troupe of Southside Theatre Guild\, open their too
 lkit to anyone who wants to learn the form — games\, scene work\, and th
 e confidence to say yes-and out loud. The workshops are free and family-fr
 iendly\, and the series runs Sundays through September 6. Participants are
  invited to perform before a real audience in a showcase on September 13. 
 Register at sidekicks@stgplays.com.
