CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:A new Atlanta comedy: 100 fast-food faithful camp overnight fo
 r free combos\, and something goes wrong.\n\nA new comedy from Atlanta pla
 ywright Kira Rockwell (Oh\, To Be Pure Again): on the eve of a beloved fas
 t-food chain's grand opening\, a hundred devotees camp overnight in the pa
 rking lot to win a year of free large combos. Someone among them is stirri
 ng up trouble\, and Jade\, the brand-new store manager\, has to root out t
 he saboteur before her flock descends into chaos. Lisa Adler directs for H
 orizon Theatre. Runs through September 20.
