DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260925T213000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1257@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Adam Gwon's sung-through musical about four New Yorkers chasin
 g fulfillment\, love\, and the occasional cab.\n\nAdam Gwon's sung-through
  chamber musical follows four New Yorkers — Claire\, Jason\, Warren\, an
 d Deb — whose ordinary lives keep intersecting in a city of 8.3 million 
 stories. Across 21 songs\, they hunt for fulfillment\, love\, and cabs\, a
 nd find their small moments adding up in unexpected ways. Presented by Arc
 adia Theater\, the Alpharetta community company.
GEO:34.0765277;-84.2884766
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Arcadia Theater\, 180 Academy St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.simpletix.com/e/ordinary-days-tickets-280877
END:VEVENT
