DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261016T220000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1608@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:David Lindsay-Abaire's comedy of two mismatched retirement-hom
 e roommates and the prank war that spirals between them.\n\nDavid Lindsay-
 Abaire's comedy set in a shared room at the Bristol Place Senior Living Fa
 cility\, where the cantankerous Abby wants her sunny upper-floor quarters 
 to herself and the relentlessly cheerful new arrival Marilyn refuses to bu
 dge. What starts as a bet between the two women spirals into increasingly 
 outrageous pranks\, and each round unearths secrets both would prefer stay
 ed buried. From Stage Door Theatre.
GEO:33.9447222;-84.3319444
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Stage Door Theatre\, 5339 Chamblee Dunwoody Rd
STATUS:CONFIRMED
