CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Mary Shelley's gothic tale onstage: a scientist\, the creature
  he abandons\, and the reckoning between them.\n\nA stage adaptation of Ma
 ry Shelley's 1818 novel. Victor Frankenstein stitches life together from t
 he dead\, recoils from what he's made\, and flees\; the abandoned creature
 \, left to learn the world alone\, goes looking for his maker. From Pumpho
 use Players\, one of Georgia's oldest continuously operating community the
 atres\, performing in a 70-seat house where nobody sits far from the monst
 er.
