BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:A Christmas Carol
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261114T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261114T161500
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-194@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Dickens's Scrooge-and-three-ghosts classic in David H. Bell's 
 adaptation with live music\, from the Alliance Theatre.\n\nCharles Dickens
 's 1843 tale of Ebenezer Scrooge\, the miser visited by the ghosts of Chri
 stmas Past\, Present\, and Yet to Come on a single night of reckoning. The
