BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:It's a Wonderful Life: A Live Radio Play
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261211T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261211T214500
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1157@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Joe Landry's radio-play staging of the 1946 Capra classic\, co
 mplete with live foley sound effects and music.\n\nJoe Landry's adaptation
  reframes the 1946 Frank Capra film as a 1940s radio broadcast: a small en
 semble of actors plays every citizen of Bedford Falls\, with sound effects
  and music made live on stage. The story is the one you know from the movi
 e\, where George Bailey hits bottom on Christmas Eve and an angel shows hi
 m what the town would look like if he had never been born. From Merely Pla
 yers\, and family-friendly.
GEO:33.9031178;-84.2776526
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Merely Players Presents\, 3785 King Ave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.merelyplayerspresents.com/event-details/its-a-wonderful-li
 fe-a-live-radio-play-2026-12-11-19-30
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:A Christmas Story: The Musical
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261211T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261211T213000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1272@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Ralphie's quest for a Red Ryder BB gun\, sung: the Pasek and P
 aul musical of the 1983 holiday film.\n\nThe 1983 movie that runs on a loo
 p every December\, turned Broadway musical with songs by Benj Pasek and Ju
 stin Paul (later of Dear Evan Hansen) and a book by Joseph Robinette. Nine
 -year-old Ralphie Parker schemes toward the one gift every adult swears wi
 ll shoot his eye out: an Official Red Ryder carbine-action BB gun. The leg
  lamp\, the tongue on the flagpole\, and the pink bunny suit all make it o
 nstage\, in a score The New York Times called "likable" and "perky." From 
 Arcadia Theater.
GEO:34.0765277;-84.2884766
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Arcadia Theater\, 180 Academy St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.simpletix.com/e/christmas-story-the-musical-tickets-279858
END:VEVENT
