BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Charles Dickens' A Christmas Carol
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261217T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261217T213500
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1501@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Dickens' ghost story told by a handful of actors\, with song\,
  an Atlanta Shakespeare Company holiday tradition of 20-plus years.\n\nJ. 
 Tony Brown's adaptation of Dickens' 1843 novella\, a fixture of the Atlant
 a Shakespeare Company's December calendar for more than two decades\, this
  year in a staging by Kati Grace Kirby. The approach is storytelling rathe
 r than spectacle: a small group of performers\, with a bit of song\, follo
 ws the miser Ebenezer Scrooge from his counting house through a Christmas 
 Eve visited by three ghosts and a certain small boy named Tiny Tim. The pl
 ayhouse's dinner-table seating means food and drink arrive during the perf
 ormance.
GEO:33.768171;-84.3851523
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Shakespeare Tavern Playhouse\, 499 Peachtree St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.shakespearetavern.com/on-stage/company/charles-dickens-a-c
 hristmas-carol
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Winter Wonderettes
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261217T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261217T220000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1619@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Roger Bean's holiday sequel to The Marvelous Wonderettes: girl
 -group harmonies at a hardware store party\, and Santa's gone missing.\n\n
 A holiday installment of Roger Bean's Marvelous Wonderettes jukebox musica
 ls\, with the four girls in tight harmony providing the entertainment at H
 arper's Hardware annual holiday party. When Santa turns up missing\, they 
 improvise their way to saving the night. The setlist leans on seasonal sta
 ndards like "Santa Claus Is Comin' to Town\," "Jingle Bell Rock\," and "Ru
 n\, Rudolph\, Run." From Stage Door Theatre.
GEO:33.9447222;-84.3319444
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Stage Door Theatre\, 5339 Chamblee Dunwoody Rd
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://ci.ovationtix.com/36385/performance/11825791/selecttickets
END:VEVENT
