 ses custody of his kids in a messy divorce\, invents Euphegenia Doubtfire\
 , a kindly Scottish nanny\, to stay in their lives. Songs come from Wayne 
 and Karey Kirkpatrick\, the songwriting team behind Something Rotten!\, wi
 th Karey Kirkpatrick and John O'Farrell sharing book duties. Four-time Ton
 y winner Jerry Zaks directs. A national touring production\, presented as 
 part of the Broadway in Atlanta series.
