BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:A Whole Weekend of Out of a Hat
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270108T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270108T204500
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1505@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Improv Comedy
DESCRIPTION:Shakespeare roulette: the play and every role drawn from a hat
  minutes before curtain.\n\nThe Atlanta Shakespeare Company's resident act
 ors perform a full Shakespeare play without knowing which one until moment
 s before the show — the title comes out of a hat\, and roles are assigne
 d two minutes to curtain. Part improv\, mostly Shakespeare\, entirely depe
 ndent on nerve and a deep memory for verse. Performed tavern-style\, with 
 table seating and food and drink service during the show. These Out of a H
 at nights tend to sell out.
GEO:33.768171;-84.3851523
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Shakespeare Tavern Playhouse\, 499 Peachtree St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.shakespearetavern.com/on-stage/company/a-whole-weekend-of-
 out-of-a-hat
END:VEVENT
