BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:BOOP! The Musical
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270112T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270112T220000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1720@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Betty Boop trades her black-and-white cartoon world for presen
 t-day New York in this touring Broadway musical comedy.\n\nBetty Boop\, ne
 arly a century into cartoon stardom\, wants one ordinary day off. Instead\
 , Grampy's teleporter drops her out of her black-and-white world and into 
 present-day New York\, where full color\, a jazz musician named Dwayne\, a
 nd a Comic Con crowd that already knows her face are waiting. Jerry Mitche
 ll (Kinky Boots\, Hairspray) directs and choreographs\, with a score by po
 p hitmaker David Foster and a book by Bob Martin (The Drowsy Chaperone). A
  national touring production of the musical that ran on Broadway in 2025.
GEO:33.7726136;-84.3853395
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Fox Theatre\, 660 Peachtree St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://foxtheatre.evenue.net/cgi-bin/ncommerce3/SEGetGroupList?groupC
 ode=BOO&linkID=fta&shopperContext=&caller=&appCode=
END:VEVENT
