UID:occ-1587@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Improv Comedy
DESCRIPTION:Unscripted comedy from the Southside Sidekicks\, built on the 
 spot from audience suggestions.\n\nNothing is scripted: the Southside Side
 kicks make the scenes up as they go\, steered by whatever the audience thr
 ows at them\, and the title suggests the crowd gets a say in where the nig
 ht wanders. The Sidekicks are the in-house improv troupe of Southside Thea
 tre Guild\, an all-volunteer community theatre running since 1973.
