CATEGORIES:Improv Comedy
DESCRIPTION:Wizard-school-themed improv night from the Southside Sidekicks
 \, Southside Theatre Guild's in-house comedy troupe.\n\nThe Southside Side
 kicks\, Southside Theatre Guild's in-house improv troupe\, take the wizard
 -school premise as their playground for a night of scenes and games built 
 on the spot from audience suggestions. Nothing is scripted\, so what happe
 ns depends on what the room throws at them.
