DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270221T220000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-259@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:A world-premiere musical: twenty years on\, a disenchanted gro
 wn Alice tries to find Wonderland again — and lands in Neverland instead
 .\n\nA new Alliance musical from Phil Kenny and Reston Williams. Two decad
 es after the rabbit hole\, Alice's life has come apart\; chasing the happi
 ness she remembers\, she sets out for Wonderland and crash-lands somewhere
  far more dangerous. A story about reclaiming childhood and what it costs 
 to never grow up.
GEO:33.7893845;-84.3846553
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Woodruff Arts Center\, 1280 Peachtree St NE
