BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Clean House
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270409T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270409T213000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1704@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Sarah Ruhl's whimsical comedy about a Brazilian housekeeper wh
 o'd rather craft the perfect joke than clean.\n\nSarah Ruhl's play\, a 200
 5 Pulitzer finalist\, starts with a mess: Lane\, a doctor\, has hired Mati
 lde\, a housekeeper who dreams of being a comedian and refuses to clean. L
 ane's sister Virginia\, who finds cleaning a calling\, secretly takes over
  the housework\, and the discoveries in the laundry pull the whole househo
 ld somewhere stranger and sadder. Variety praised its "screwy poetry and p
 enetrating wisdom." Presented by Merely Players.
GEO:33.9031178;-84.2776526
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Merely Players Presents\, 3785 King Ave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.merelyplayerspresents.com/event-details/the-clean-house-04
 -09-27
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Great American Trailer Park Musical
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270409T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270409T223000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1210@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Nehls and Kelso's raunchy comedy of a stripper on the run and 
 one very stuck marriage in a Florida trailer park.\n\nDavid Nehls and Bets
 y Kelso's Off-Broadway comedy set in Armadillo Acres\, a trailer park in S
 tarke\, Florida. Jeannie hasn't left her trailer since her son was abducte
 d two decades ago\; her tollbooth-collector husband Norbert hopes annivers
 ary Ice Capades tickets will finally coax her out. Then Pippi\, a stripper
  fleeing a marker-sniffing ex-boyfriend\, moves in and complicates everyth
 ing. From Pumphouse Players.
GEO:34.1644344;-84.7971239
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Pumphouse Players\, 114 W Main St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/the-great-american-trailer-park-musical-t
 ickets-1989768581390
END:VEVENT
