SUMMARY:The Great American Trailer Park Musical
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270410T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270410T223000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1211@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Nehls and Kelso's raunchy comedy of a stripper on the run and 
 one very stuck marriage in a Florida trailer park.\n\nDavid Nehls and Bets
 y Kelso's Off-Broadway comedy set in Armadillo Acres\, a trailer park in S
 tarke\, Florida. Jeannie hasn't left her trailer since her son was abducte
 d two decades ago\; her tollbooth-collector husband Norbert hopes annivers
 ary Ice Capades tickets will finally coax her out. Then Pippi\, a stripper
  fleeing a marker-sniffing ex-boyfriend\, moves in and complicates everyth
 ing. From Pumphouse Players.
GEO:34.1644344;-84.7971239
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Pumphouse Players\, 114 W Main St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/the-great-american-trailer-park-musical-t
 ickets-1989768581390
END:VEVENT
