  company has been at it since 1977.\n\nA fundraising gala celebrating a mi
 lestone: Theatrical Outfit's 50th season. The downtown Atlanta company\, f
 ounded in 1977\, produces a mix of classic and contemporary plays alongsid
 e new-play development programs like Launchpad\, and proceeds from the eve
