BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Notebook
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270418T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270418T210000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1744@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:The Broadway musical of Nicholas Sparks's tearjerker romance\,
  with songs by Ingrid Michaelson\, on national tour.\n\nNicholas Sparks's 
 1996 novel — already one of the highest-grossing romantic film dramas ev
 er adapted — reworked as a Broadway musical\, with a score by singer-son
 gwriter Ingrid Michaelson and a script by playwright Bekah Brunstetter. Al
 lie and Noah come from different worlds and spend a lifetime finding their
  way back to each other\; the musical splits each role among three actors 
 playing them at different ages. A national touring production\, following 
 the show's 2024 Broadway run.
GEO:33.7726136;-84.3853395
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Fox Theatre\, 660 Peachtree St NE
