BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Mama Bear Repertory: The Winter's Tale and Mel Konner’s Sixt
 een Springs or Four Loves
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270527T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270527T214500
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1572@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Shakespeare's late romance in repertory with a new Atlanta pla
 y filling in its sixteen-year gap.\n\nA repertory pairing from the Atlanta
  Shakespeare Company: Shakespeare's rarely staged late romance alongside a
  brand-new companion piece. In The Winter's Tale\, a king's unfounded jeal
 ousy costs him his wife\, his children\, and his best friend before the st
 ory thaws into pastoral comedy and magic. On alternating dates\, Sixteen S
 prings or Four Loves\, by Atlanta playwright Mel Konner\, dramatizes the s
 ixteen years Shakespeare skips: the abandoned princess raised by shepherds
 \, and Antigonus surviving his famous bear. The repertory runs through May
  30.
GEO:33.768171;-84.3851523
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Shakespeare Tavern Playhouse\, 499 Peachtree St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.shakespearetavern.com/on-stage/company/the-mama-bear-reper
 tory-the-winters-tale-and-mel-konner-s-sixteen-springs-or-four-loves
END:VEVENT
