UID:occ-1301@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Dahl's telekinetic bookworm takes on the fearsome Miss Trunchb
 ull\, with songs by Tim Minchin.\n\nDennis Kelly and Tim Minchin's musical
  adaptation of Roald Dahl's novel about Matilda Wormwood\, a brilliant lit
 tle girl saddled with crooked parents and a child-hating headmistress who 
 invents punishments for sport. Matilda fights back with wit\, a fierce lov
 e of books\, and a psychokinetic trick or two\, finding an ally in her gen
 tle teacher Miss Honey. First staged by the Royal Shakespeare Company\, th
 e show won a record seven Olivier Awards in 2012. This production comes fr
 om Arcadia Theater\, the community company continuing three decades of the
 atre-making in its space.
GEO:34.0765277;-84.2884766
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
