BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Stand Up for Improv - Improvised Stand-Up Show
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270612
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270613
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1598@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Improv Comedy
DESCRIPTION:Stand-up with no prepared material: comics improvise their set
 s live from audience suggestions.\n\nA mash-up of two comedy forms: the pe
 rformers take the stand-up mic\, but every joke is invented on the spot\, 
 built from whatever the audience throws at them. No script\, no tested mat
 erial\, no safety net. Presented by Southside Theatre Guild\, an all-volun
 teer community theatre running since 1973.
GEO:33.5672762;-84.5821546
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Southside Theatre Guild\, 20 W Campbellton St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://tockify.com/stgevents/detail/1065/1812772800000
END:VEVENT
