BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Children
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270612T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270612T213000
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1059@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Lucy Kirkwood's darkly comic thriller: two retired nuclear phy
 sicists\, a colleague back after 38 years\, and old debts coming due.\n\nI
 n a cottage on the British coast\, two married\, retired nuclear physicist
 s live quietly in the wake of a disaster. Then a former colleague reappear
 s after 38 years\, and the couple's careful equilibrium starts to crack. L
 ucy Kirkwood's 2016 thriller\, funnier than its premise suggests\, asks wh
 at one generation owes the one that follows\; it was a hit in London and o
 n Broadway\, and in 2019 Guardian writers ranked it third among the greate
 st theatrical works since 2000. Presented by Theatrical Outfit.
GEO:33.757035;-84.389486
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Theatrical Outfit\, 84 Luckie St NW
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Guess Who's Coming to Dinner
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270612T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270612T214500
DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1177@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Todd Kreidler's stage adaptation of the 1967 film: a daughter'
 s surprise fiancé tests her progressive parents' ideals.\n\nTodd Kreidler
  adapts the 1967 film that starred Sidney Poitier\, Spencer Tracy\, and Ka
 tharine Hepburn\, released the same year the Supreme Court struck down ban
 s on interracial marriage in Loving v. Virginia. A liberal couple's daught
 er comes home unannounced with a new fiancé\, and a celebratory dinner tu
 rns into a long night of the family arguing with its own principles about 
 love\, race\, and acceptance. Funnier than its subject suggests\, and poin
 ted where it counts. Presented by Merely Players.
GEO:33.9031178;-84.2776526
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Merely Players Presents\, 3785 King Ave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.merelyplayerspresents.com/event-details/guess-whos-coming-
 to-dinner-2027-06-12-19-30
END:VEVENT
