DTSTAMP:20260708T065306Z
UID:occ-1181@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Todd Kreidler's stage adaptation of the 1967 film: a daughter'
 s surprise fiancé tests her progressive parents' ideals.\n\nTodd Kreidler
  adapts the 1967 film that starred Sidney Poitier\, Spencer Tracy\, and Ka
 tharine Hepburn\, released the same year the Supreme Court struck down ban
 s on interracial marriage in Loving v. Virginia. A liberal couple's daught
 er comes home unannounced with a new fiancé\, and a celebratory dinner tu
 rns into a long night of the family arguing with its own principles about 
 love\, race\, and acceptance. Funnier than its subject suggests\, and poin
 ted where it counts. Presented by Merely Players.
GEO:33.9031178;-84.2776526
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T063625Z
LOCATION:Merely Players Presents\, 3785 King Ave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.merelyplayerspresents.com/event-details/guess-whos-coming-
 to-dinner-2027-06-20-17-00
END:VEVENT
